The Debian [1] package for the Apophenia Statistical C Library
is currently maintained by the Debian Science Team [2,3]:
the git repository for the apophenia Debian package is at Alioth [4].

To install the Apophenia standard suite on Debian based systems:
	apt-get update
	apt-get install apophenia-bin apophenia-doc

For a complete and up-to-date list of Apophenia related packages,
you may search at the distribution webpage dedicated to Packages [5,6].

[1] https://www.debian.org/
[2] https://wiki.debian.org/DebianScience
[3] https://qa.debian.org/developer.php?login=debian-science-maintainers@lists.alioth.debian.org
[4] http://anonscm.debian.org/cgit/debian-science/packages/apophenia.git/
[5] https://packages.debian.org/search?keywords=apophenia
[6] http://packages.ubuntu.com/search?keywords=apophenia
